    {
      "id": "PopularPost78813",
      "post_content": "If you attach this to your opponent's creature, **you** still have to sacrifice a creature: read the text of [Recumbent Bliss](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Recumbent Bliss). I'm confused, then why is this any good?",
      "posted_by": "Edrocks006",
