      "id": "PopularPost168336",
      "post_content": "Wizards totally missed a chance to make this a fair and interesting card: '...has trample and \"at the beginning of your upkeep, sacrifice a creature\" '.  \nThen it could double as high-stakes removal.  \nAs it is, it's just the (admittedly several years newer) [Demonic Appetite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Demonic Appetite), plus trample for 2 more mana.  \n  \nHmm, DacenOctavio's Donate idea from the Demonic Appetite discussion page WOULD actually work here! Use [Puca's Mischief](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Puca's Mischief) or [Confusion in the Ranks](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Confusion in the Ranks)...",
      "posted_by": "HuntingDrake",
